Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏降临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算黑暗吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那持续闪烁的星屑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像朝阳那般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围绕封印着雷藏的冥王之壶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹得天翻地覆的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易壶到我手里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可关键的事尚未弄清
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:01:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 杰路和波克塔都发狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 每个家伙都…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Xeno 复活的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等等 那边的小动物王子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 别跟过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了雷藏大人的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔走这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也是在这附近跟丢的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个雾 没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离塔夫拉希亚很近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等这附近的雾散了再找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么悠闲可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔说不定马上就让雷藏复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏大概会随便找点理由拖延时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿走壶的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏好像也在复活和毁灭间犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像感觉和欧泽鲁一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁也是一边保护壶一边想破坏它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什么联系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个壶绝对有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在莉娜他们来到前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让雷藏复活 解开大家的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有月光的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没法解开人们的封印的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我施加了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在月光穿过天空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳升起来之前举行仪式的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们就无法从沉睡中苏醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那即便现在抓紧也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能等晚上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:05:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你的表情这么忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然拿着壶到了塔夫拉希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一想到雷藏复活需要自己的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会迷惑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是对的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就毋须迷惑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类不是那么简单就能抛开一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人偶是不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这个国家的王子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受杜拉姆病之苦的子们们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为王子却无法拯救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这次一定要做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人们快乐地生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让笑容充满塔夫拉希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这比什么都重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要牺牲自己的身体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让雷藏复活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开大家的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底他是杰路刚帝士和大家所说的那种恶徒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我所相信的雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的灵魂转移到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我解开封印
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这个国家复活为止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想见见他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲眼来确认
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见雷藏大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 神殿是在这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 在右边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 左边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前来过这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多人 居然没一个记着怎么走 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时是波克塔带的路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还会再来一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是有点预感的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是雷藏还没复活就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一躲在那里听了波克塔的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很困扰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了啊 休闲魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要让你说出冥王之壶的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 不凑巧啊 那个果然是秘密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直保守秘密也不太好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就告诉你们神殿的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 那个那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地下墓室里 封印着塔夫拉希亚的民众吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔的身体也沉睡在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 纹丝不动的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是塔夫拉希亚最神圣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是陌生人可以轻易进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是早说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 以前是由波克塔打开门的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用魔法打飞它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可沉睡着数千上万的灵魂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁莽行事的话 后果很严重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是魔族的万金油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就应该打开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能帮你们的也就这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就请大家自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的到底是什么 杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 那是秘密啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己想要壶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却告诉我们神殿的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我们是老交情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要说的话 因为有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键的都没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这下我确信了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个壶除了雷藏之外 还有些其他东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才让我们去追那个壶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等于多上一层保险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要让他复活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制着复杂的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来决定自己的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此不同的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界还有善恶的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若根据感情而行动是善则最好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可有时也会成恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听从雷藏大人的命令便是善
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外都是恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类要是能这么容易想通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就会轻松点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时也弄不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓人类的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你弄糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会去尝试考虑有关人类的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果因此能帮上雷藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者能更接近雷藏大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 欧泽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是顺着这条路一直走下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 只有一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有岔路的话可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…分岔了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 之前来时只有一条路的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概和波克塔一起时没注意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这个建筑原本就是迷宫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 毕竟是个神圣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎…怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即然这样 烈火…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚 不能用魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想和你一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了 之前一直沉默不言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会现在又说不想复活了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不想复活 那是撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能保证一定能解开塔夫拉希亚的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那样 你可就白白失去肉体了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我是塔夫拉希亚的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要赌这个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这里怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于…终于能拯救大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁 把壶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想复活雷藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才雷藏也说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要复活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 欧泽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管如何 我都要拯救塔夫拉希亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 看来只好由我来阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 冥王之壶能交给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总是一次又一次的盯上这个壶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们魔族而言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不再需要雷藏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不凑巧 我并不能回答这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为上司会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我更不会交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不想动粗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可奈何了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才只是稍做恐吓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还来得及啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔 把壶交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不想让雷藏复活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要对塔夫拉希亚见死不救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这只是我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个壶一定另有隐情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没弄清楚之前 不能让他复活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用这些话来吓唬我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且用你的身体做宿主的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要一辈子做小动物了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早有觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 风险太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救这个国家和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈闪枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我还没说完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 冷静下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹阵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么雷藏命令你保护壶的同时破坏他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概有点头绪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 雷藏复活时会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我个人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的复活可以验证我的假设
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏选择谁做容器都与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尊重你的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意志…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类根据感情而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塔夫拉希亚的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏大人 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再见你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那是违反命令的恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想拯救我的国家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我明白 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再一事无成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让雷藏大人复活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想遵从自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在考虑人类是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过模仿人类 尝试寻找答案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许只是普通的模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和大家那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚实面对自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该说你是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 欧泽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 欧泽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你受苦了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:21:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我从未觉得痛苦过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护壶的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉自己似乎明白了雷藏大人所说的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否更接近人类了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 欧泽鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 莉娜.因巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红法师 雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以巨大的代价作为交换而复活的红法师雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.07,0:23:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那紧闭的瞳孔 在寻求什么 在诉说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 秀逗魔导士.进化-R
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterdays memory 失而复得的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看的话我会发飙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

